{
  "stem": "14737.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in that school, there were going also some Czech who lived there-- where, where an army base is where there who were Czechs, who were going also to the Russian school, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these were intelligent-- coming from intelligent families.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not born there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They remained there during because it was an army bases.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And their children-- captain's child or a colonel's child-- went to school, by the name of [INAUDIBLE] or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were more like not the peasants from the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, mainly, mainly among-- and I had friends among the Jewish students who went in the Hungarian gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were Jews, Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, non-Jews were there, but Hungarians, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wouldn't say so much that anti-Semitism was [INAUDIBLE] Russian gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't feel anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, it wasn't so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, the professor that teachers in the Hungarian gymnasiums, they were different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were from pre-World War I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were there for a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gymnasium existed since 1900, probably.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were all the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them were Jews, even teachers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were already living in Beregsaz for years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had their houses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had their families.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were more or less settled, I don't know, inside [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But here in our school were mostly who came from Ukraine after World War I.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they settled down because they ran away from the Bolsheviks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, this gymnasium is about eight years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, what we learned at the gymnasium, mostly languages-- Latin, French, and so on-- all the subject.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spent that eight years until already know something-- I started there, was 11 years old around-- I was 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here it comes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was during the regime of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
